content.rendered:
Directed by Hadi ali Abar. Gill Shubham.

Written by Aleena Chouhan. Reena Daniel. Bilal Qureshi. Pankaj Uniyal. Pankaj Uniyal.

Cast Muntazir Ahmad. Kushi Anand(Kushi Thakur). Vikrant Anand(Ranveer Thakur). Sai Ballal(Dharmveer Thakur (as Ranveer Father)).Sapna Choudhary. Shunty Dugria(Jay).Ajeet Goswami.Anju Jadhav.Zuber K. Khan. Kushi(Dharmveer Daughter / Khushi). Ratnesh Mani(Inspector Ranjeet SIngh Walia).Neel Motwani.Ansh Pandit.Rohit Rajawat. Shivani Sopori(Ranveer’s mother (as Shivaani Sopuri))

Languages Hindi. English.

Producers Amit Chandra. Joyal Daniel. Ravinder Singh. Sunbir. Vishal Vats.

Production Share Happiness Films.
